*Pain: Mechanisms and Management. F.A. Davis & Co (1993) {{ISBN|978-0-8036-1635-6}}
*Knee Pain and Disability (Pain Series). F.A. Davis & Co (1992) {{ISBN|978-0-8036-1622-6}}
